com.ge.dspmicro.machinegateway.api.adapter

Class AbstractSubscriptionMachineAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ge.dspmicro.machinegateway.api.adapter.AbstractSubscriptionMachineAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMachineAdapter, ISubscriptionMachineAdapter

    public abstract class AbstractSubscriptionMachineAdapter
extends Object
implements ISubscriptionMachineAdapter
    The functionality abstracted in this class is a mechanism for services that monitor a selection of subscriptions that are provided by the adapters in the Machine Gateway to be updated whenever those subscriptions are added or removed.
